title: The Deep Dive & How Did This Get Made? Crossover: Love On A Leash
description:
This week we have a treat for our Deep Divers and giving you all a first listen of the crossover podcast of the century. June, Jessica, Paul Scheer and Jason Mantzoukas cover the 2011 film, Love On A Leash. June and Jessica ask the same questions you expect, “do you find your dog attractive” and “what are the proper packing cubes to use”? June questions the details of using a 'hot spot' and her Jessica and Jason break down what we can only call "dog boudoir" photos. Remember Deep Divers do NOT sleep on Kyle. 


More info for Plan C pills https://www.plancpills.org/


 

Visit the Pinterest Board pinterest.com/thedeepdive

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod

Jessica St. Clair @Jessica_StClair on Twitter @stclairjessica on Instagram
